14:["$","section","3. When we share information",{"className":"card p-5 sm:p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-black text-[var(--text-primary)]","children":"3. When we share information"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-3 space-y-3","children":[["$","p","We do not sell your personal information. We share information only when it is necessary to provide the service, comply with the law, or protect Mechi, our users, and the integrity of competition on the platform.",{"className":"text-sm leading-7 text-[var(--text-secondary)] sm:text-base","children":"We do not sell your personal information. We share information only when it is necessary to provide the service, comply with the law, or protect Mechi, our users, and the integrity of competition on the platform."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-[var(--text-secondary)] sm:text-base","children":[["$","li","With service providers that help us host the app, send emails, analyze usage, store files, or support customer operations.",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--brand-teal)]"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"With service providers that help us host the app, send emails, analyze usage, store files, or support customer operations."}]]}],["$","li","With payment providers and financial partners that process subscription or tournament transactions on our behalf.",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--brand-teal)]"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"With payment providers and financial partners that process subscription or tournament transactions on our behalf."}]]}],["$","li","With other users to the extent your public profile, match results, rankings, tournament entries, or shared links are visible inside the product.",{"className":"flex gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--brand-tea